{
  "title": "Decadent Irish Fish Chowder",
  "description": "A rich and creamy fish chowder featuring duck fat and a blend of cheeses, perfect for a midnight craving. This pescatarian-friendly dish is sure to become a favorite.",
  "cuisine": "Irish",
  "diet": [
    "pescatarian"
